Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.64,English,,0,0,0,,that no one would want to ever associate with Russia again.\N{\rChinese}那时没有人愿意再与俄罗斯结缘。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay so that was the argument back\N{\rChinese}好的，回到那个论点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.88,English,,0,0,0,,then and today what we have seen is\N{\rChinese}然后今天我们看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.96,English,,0,0,0,,that the complete opposite has happened.\N{\rChinese}那件事发生后，完全相反的事发生了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.42,English,,0,0,0,,Okay so\N{\rChinese}好了，回到那个论点。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:16.34,English,,0,0,0,,first of all Russia has basically won the war\N{\rChinese}首先，俄罗斯基本赢得了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:20.06,English,,0,0,0,,and it's won the war because of attrition right?\N{\rChinese}这场战争之所以赢得，是因为消耗战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:25.52,English,,0,0,0,,Ukraine has lost maybe 500,000 men in this war\N{\rChinese}乌克兰在这场战争中损失约五十万兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.20,English,,0,0,0,,so they have no more manpower.\N{\rChinese}于是他们就没有足够的人力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.88,English,,0,0,0,,If you don't have manpower you're not going to be able to fight this war.\N{\rChinese}如果没有足够的人力，你就无法在这场战争中作战。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:35.66,English,,0,0,0,,So this war has basically been lost and Russia is dominant.\N{\rChinese}于是这场战争基本上已失，俄罗斯则占据主导。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:40.06,English,,0,0,0,,Russia has basically achieved its main strategic objectives\N{\rChinese}俄罗斯基本实现了其主要战略目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:44.34,English,,0,0,0,,which are which is basically the Donetsk region in eastern Ukraine.\N{\rChinese}即在乌克兰东部的顿涅茨克地区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:50.12,English,,0,0,0,,Secondly, not only has the Russian economy not been destroyed\N{\rChinese}其次，俄国经济不仅没有被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:54.06,English,,0,0,0,,but it's been doing extremely well okay\N{\rChinese}而且表现得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:56.38,English,,0,0,0,,and the reason why is that\N{\rChinese}原因就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.26,English,,0,0,0,,ultimately all economies, China, India,\N{\rChinese}最终，所有经济体，像中国、印度、欧洲、非洲、中东，都需要资源才能让经济运转。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.80,English,,0,0,0,,Europe, Africa,\N{\rChinese}最终，所有经济体，像中国、印度、欧洲、非洲、中东，都需要资源才能让经济运转。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:09.76,English,,0,0,0,,Middle East, they all need resources in order for their economies to work.\N{\rChinese}最终，所有经济体，像中国、印度、欧洲、非洲、中东，都需要资源才能让经济运转。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.56,English,,0,0,0,,You need oil, you need food.\N{\rChinese}你需要石油，你需要粮食。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.92,English,,0,0,0,,And Russia has a lot of oil and food.\N{\rChinese}俄国有大量石油和粮食。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.64,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why countries have been going to Russia\N{\rChinese}这就是各国去俄国的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.04,English,,0,0,0,,and making side deals.\N{\rChinese}并且做了边际交易。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.10,English,,0,0,0,,Also, Russia has been transitioning to a war economy,\N{\rChinese}此外，俄国已转向战时经济，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.38,English,,0,0,0,,so its manufacturing base has been increasing.\N{\rChinese}其制造业基地也在增长。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.88,English,,0,0,0,,So overall, the economy has been doing a lot better.\N{\rChinese}整体来看，经济表现大幅提升。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.24,English,,0,0,0,,U.S. sanctions have not been working.\N{\rChinese}美国制裁效果不明显。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:37.90,English,,0,0,0,,The third of all, NATO has become more divided\N{\rChinese}第三点，北约内部分化加剧。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.54,English,,0,0,0,,and less united.\N{\rChinese}并且更不统一。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Because Germany,\N{\rChinese}为什么？因为德国，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.76,English,,0,0,0,,which is the most powerful country in Europe right now,\N{\rChinese}它是目前欧洲最强大的国家。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.72,English,,0,0,0,,is completely dependent on Russian\N{\rChinese}完全依赖俄方资源来驱动其经济。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.24,English,,0,0,0,,resources to fuel its economy.\N{\rChinese}这就是德国经济的运作方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,That's how the German economy works.\N{\rChinese}That's how the German economy works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.52,English,,0,0,0,,It's a manufacturing economy.\N{\rChinese}它是一个制造业经济体。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.22,English,,0,0,0,,It takes cheap Russian gas,\N{\rChinese}它使用便宜的俄气，
