Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.46,English,,0,0,0,,these three fundamental weaknesses in the Empire,\N{\rChinese}这些帝国的三大基本弱点，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.08,English,,0,0,0,,and if it is true that\N{\rChinese}如果这是真的的话
