Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:22.26,English,,0,0,0,,who is abetting Hamas, then\N{\rChinese}who is abettingHamas, then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.38,English,,0,0,0,,we can predict that Putin will continue to destroy the American Empire.\N{\rChinese}我们可以预测普京会继续摧毁美国帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.74,English,,0,0,0,,So if it is true that Putin's intention is to destroy the American Empire, then we can predict that Putin's intention is to destroy the American Empire. certain things, okay? The first thing that\N{\rChinese}于是如果普京的意图确实是摧毁美国帝国，那么我们可以预测普京的意图就是摧毁美国帝国。先说几件事，好吗？第一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.82,English,,0,0,0,,he will do is he will\N{\rChinese}他将要做的第一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.76,English,,0,0,0,,drag on the Ukraine war.\N{\rChinese}拖延乌克兰战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.82,English,,0,0,0,,So he will not end it,\N{\rChinese}于是他不会结束它，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.50,English,,0,0,0,,he will not seek peace,\N{\rChinese}他也不会寻求和平。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:44.18,English,,0,0,0,,he will not negotiate peace terms, he will continue to drag it on,\N{\rChinese}他不会谈判和平条款，他会继续拖延它。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.68,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Why would he do that?\N{\rChinese}好？他为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.70,English,,0,0,0,,Why not just declare victory?\N{\rChinese}为什么不直接宣布胜利呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.54,English,,0,0,0,,Or why not just negotiate peace?\N{\rChinese}或者直接谈判和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.96,English,,0,0,0,,Why would he do that? Why not just declare victory? Or why not just negotiate peace? orig Why would he want to drag it on?\N{\rChinese}他为什么要这么做？为什么不直接宣布胜利？或者直接谈判和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah, the Russian people will constantly be at war, but\N{\rChinese}好的，俄国人民会一直处于战争之中，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:14.82,English,,0,0,0,,then the question then is, why would he drag it on and not expand it, right?\N{\rChinese}然后问题是，为什么他要拖延而不扩张，没错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.76,English,,0,0,0,,He wants to drag it on, but he doesn't want to expand it.\N{\rChinese}他想拖延，却不想扩张。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.64,English,,0,0,0,,Expand it means he attacks Poland.\N{\rChinese}扩张就是攻击波兰。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.90,English,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to do that, he just wants to drag it on.\N{\rChinese}他不想这么做，只是想拖延而已。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:26.20,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Yeah,\N{\rChinese}为什么？嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.56,English,,0,0,0,,okay, so the reason is that\N{\rChinese}好，原因是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.98,English,,0,0,0,,Ukraine is turning out to be a black hole for NATO.\N{\rChinese}乌克兰正变成北约的黑洞。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.12,English,,0,0,0,,NATO and the United States is putting in all this money,\N{\rChinese}北约和美国投入了大量资金、武器和人力。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.14,English,,0,0,0,,weapons, and manpower,\N{\rChinese}weapons, and manpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.70,English,,0,0,0,,and it's just losing it all, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且它正全失，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.64,English,,0,0,0,,So, in other words,\N{\rChinese}所以，换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:50.56,English,,0,0,0,,Ukraine is a battlefield to increase American debt\N{\rChinese}乌克兰是提升美债的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.46,English,,0,0,0,,and create civil discord among NATO and America, okay?\N{\rChinese}并在北约与美之间制造内战，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.84,English,,0,0,0,,Germany does not want to fight this war.\N{\rChinese}德国不想再打这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.84,English,,0,0,0,,Germany wants out, you understand?\N{\rChinese}德国想退出，你懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.08,English,,0,0,0,,So as long as this war keeps on going,\N{\rChinese}只要这场战争继续下去，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.50,English,,0,0,0,,it's gonna create more friction between NATO and the United States, and that's what Putin wants.\N{\rChinese}它会在北约与美国之间产生更多摩擦，而这正是普京想要的。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.34,English,,0,0,0,,But if Putin attacks Poland,\N{\rChinese}但如果普京进攻波兰，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,then all NATO is forced to fight him, okay?\N{\rChinese}然后所有北约都被迫去跟他打仗，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.72,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So he does not want to expand the war,\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？所以他不想把战争扩大，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.70,English,,0,0,0,,he just wants the war to maintain a status quo and\N{\rChinese}他只是想让战争保持现状，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.82,English,,0,0,0,,for it to drag on, okay?\N{\rChinese}为了让它持续下去，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.42,English,,0,0,0,,So that's the first prediction.\N{\rChinese}于是这是第一个预测。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.18,English,,0,0,0,,Second is that\N{\rChinese}第二个是……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.36,English,,0,0,0,,to control the situation in Ukraine,\N{\rChinese}为掌控乌克兰局势，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.46,English,,0,0,0,,he needs America to fight another war, okay?\N{\rChinese}他需要美国再打一场战争，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.62,English,,0,0,0,,He needs to distract America, and the distraction will be Iran.\N{\rChinese}他需要分散美国，目标是伊朗。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.92,English,,0,0,0,,Remember how, for the past few classes,\N{\rChinese}记得吗，过去几节课我们讨论过美国想攻击伊朗的情形。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.74,English,,0,0,0,,we've been discussing how America wants to attack Iran and\N{\rChinese}we've been discussing how America wants to attack Iran and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.38,English,,0,0,0,,Iran wants revenge against America, okay?\N{\rChinese}伊朗想要报复美国，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:48.32,English,,0,0,0,,But for this to happen, what Putin needs to do is talk to Iran\N{\rChinese}但要实现这一点，普京需要做的就是与伊朗对话。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.90,English,,0,0,0,,and guarantee that\N{\rChinese}并保证
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:54.44,English,,0,0,0,,Iran will be protected by the Russian nuclear umbrella.\N{\rChinese}伊朗将被俄方的核伞所保护。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.32,English,,0,0,0,,Which means that\N{\rChinese}这意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,America will not be allowed to use nuclear weapons\N{\rChinese}美国将不被允许使用核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.54,English,,0,0,0,,when it invades Iran, because\N{\rChinese}当它入侵伊朗时，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.96,English,,0,0,0,,Putin will respond with nuclear weapons of his own, okay, does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}普京会用自己的核武器回应，好吗？这样说对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:08.64,English,,0,0,0,,So as long as Putin comes to an agreement with Iran\N{\rChinese}只要普京与伊朗达成协议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:13.18,English,,0,0,0,,and say that, I will use my nuclear weapons to protect you from US nuclear weapons,\N{\rChinese}并说我会用核武器保护你免受美方核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.32,English,,0,0,0,,then Iran will take the initiative\N{\rChinese}然后伊朗将主动出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.36,English,,0,0,0,,and start to provoke America into a wider war.\N{\rChinese}随后伊朗会挑起美方更大规模的战争
