Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.36,0:24:48.60,English,,0,0,0,,and the United States to be friends, right?\N{\rChinese}美国也要跟中国做朋友，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:52.80,English,,0,0,0,,Because China exports a lot of commodities to the United States.\N{\rChinese}因为中国向美国出口大量商品。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:54.28,English,,0,0,0,,The United States is a huge market.\N{\rChinese}美国是一个巨大的市场。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:57.38,English,,0,0,0,,The United States also provides China with a lot of technology, right?\N{\rChinese}美国也为中国提供了大量技术，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:03.62,English,,0,0,0,,And Jack asked the question, why would China want to be friends with Russia?\N{\rChinese}于是杰克问了一个问题：为什么中国想跟俄罗斯做朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:07.54,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is because China right now\N{\rChinese}答案是因为中国现在觉得被美国威胁，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:10.32,English,,0,0,0,,feels threatened by the United States, okay?\N{\rChinese}feels threatened by the United States, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.48,0:25:14.28,English,,0,0,0,,The United States is launching an economic war against China.\N{\rChinese}美国正对中国发动经济战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:19.32,English,,0,0,0,,And if you look at a map,\N{\rChinese}如果你看一张地图，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:25.44,English,,0,0,0,,okay, China is surrounded by US military bases.\N{\rChinese}好的，中国被美军基地包围。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:28.30,English,,0,0,0,,And the problem is that\N{\rChinese}问题是……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:33.34,English,,0,0,0,,China needs imports of oil\N{\rChinese}中国需要进口石油
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.34,0:25:36.06,English,,0,0,0,,and food to sustain its economy.\N{\rChinese}以及食品来支撑其经济。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.36,0:25:37.80,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.80,0:25:40.96,English,,0,0,0,,if America ever launches a embargo against China,\N{\rChinese}如果美国曾对中国实施禁运，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.30,0:25:43.94,English,,0,0,0,,China collapses, okay?\N{\rChinese}中国崩溃，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.28,0:25:48.76,English,,0,0,0,,So in other words, China needs to open up new trade routes.\N{\rChinese}换句话说，中国需要开辟新的贸易路线。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.94,0:25:52.04,English,,0,0,0,,And the best partner right now is Russia because\N{\rChinese}而现在最好的合作伙伴是俄罗斯，因为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:55.94,English,,0,0,0,,it has a lot of access to energy and oil, okay?\N{\rChinese}它有很多能源和石油的渠道，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.22,0:25:59.84,English,,0,0,0,,So right now, the situation in China is\N{\rChinese}现在，中国的局势是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.84,0:26:04.50,English,,0,0,0,,that Chinese policymakers know that the situation in China is terrible.\N{\rChinese}那时中国决策者已知局势惨烈。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.80,0:26:06.10,English,,0,0,0,,The economy has collapsed.\N{\rChinese}经济已崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.46,0:26:07.74,English,,0,0,0,,Demographics has collapsed.\N{\rChinese}人口结构已崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.46,0:26:13.22,English,,0,0,0,,China is completely dependent on the world for oil.\N{\rChinese}中国完全依赖世界的石油。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.12,0:26:17.26,English,,0,0,0,,China is extremely vulnerable right now.\N{\rChinese}中国现在极为脆弱。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:21.10,English,,0,0,0,,If America says to the world, China is our enemy,\N{\rChinese}如果美国对世界说：‘中国是我们的敌人’
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:23.72,English,,0,0,0,,then China has no choice but to find a new friend.\N{\rChinese}然后，中国只能再找一个新朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:28.62,English,,0,0,0,,And unfortunately, the only friend that China has right now is Russia, okay?\N{\rChinese}而且不幸的是，现阶段中国唯一的朋友就是俄罗斯，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.64,0:26:30.28,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:33.40,English,,0,0,0,,So, but look,\N{\rChinese}于是，先说一下，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.64,0:26:38.30,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, the geopolitical situation for China, it's really, really bad, okay?\N{\rChinese}我想说的是，中国的地缘政治形势真的非常糟糕，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.88,0:26:40.88,English,,0,0,0,,Any more questions before I continue?\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:47.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay,\N{\rChinese}好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:52.76,English,,0,0,0,,so, Selena asked a great question. Why does the United States think\N{\rChinese}于是，塞莱娜提出了一个很好的问题。美国为什么认为中国会攻击台湾？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.76,0:26:54.78,English,,0,0,0,,that China will attack Taiwan?\N{\rChinese}答案是：美国总是想发动新战争，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.06,0:26:57.24,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is that\N{\rChinese}而答案是，美国总是想发动新战争，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.24,0:27:01.20,English,,0,0,0,,America is always looking to start new wars, okay?\N{\rChinese}美国总是想发动新战争，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.42,0:27:03.06,English,,0,0,0,,It has something called a military -industrial complex.\N{\rChinese}它有一个叫做军工复合的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:06.00,English,,0,0,0,,And America is always fighting wars.\N{\rChinese}美国总是打仗。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:09.68,English,,0,0,0,,So to justify all this defense spending,\N{\rChinese}为此，美国需要为这笔防御开支做辩护，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.52,0:27:12.50,English,,0,0,0,,it needs to find new enemies.\N{\rChinese}它需要再找新的敌人来支撑，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.96,0:27:16.30,English,,0,0,0,,And it believes that\N{\rChinese}于是它便认为……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.30,0:27:19.58,English,,0,0,0,,the greatest threat to the American empire right now is China,\N{\rChinese}目前美国帝国最大的威胁是中国，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.70,0:27:22.98,English,,0,0,0,,even though, by the way, there's no evidence this is the case, okay?\N{\rChinese}顺便说一句，没证据表明如此，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:25.68,English,,0,0,0,,Right now, the relationship between the United States and\N{\rChinese}现在美中关系是……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.68,0:27:30.86,English,,0,0,0,,China is China sends America a lot of cheap goods\N{\rChinese}中国向美国发送大量低价商品
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:34.68,English,,0,0,0,,and the US gives China a lot of US dollars,\N{\rChinese}美国则给中国大量美元
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.02,0:27:38.06,English,,0,0,0,,okay? So basically what's happening is\N{\rChinese}好吧？基本上发生的事是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.06,0:27:42.72,English,,0,0,0,,that the Communist Party is storing the wealth of the Chinese people\N{\rChinese}共产党把中国人民的财富存入美国银行。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:47.18,English,,0,0,0,,in American banks. This is a great deal for both America,\N{\rChinese}这对美国、华尔街和中国共产党都是一笔大交易。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:50.50,English,,0,0,0,,Wall Street, and the Chinese Communist Party, okay?\N{\rChinese}好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.72,0:27:54.86,English,,0,0,0,,So there's no reason for these countries to be in conflict with each other,\N{\rChinese}于是这些国家之间没有必要相互冲突，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.00,0:27:57.40,English,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately, the American policymakers\N{\rChinese}但不幸的是，美国决策者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.38,0:28:02.36,English,,0,0,0,,always need an enemy to justify the\N{\rChinese}总是需要一个敌人来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.36,0:28:04.88,English,,0,0,0,,incredible amount of money they spent on defense, okay?\N{\rChinese}他们在防御上花了不可思议的金额，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.92,0:28:08.34,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay, any more questions before I continue?\N{\rChinese}这样说对吗？好了，继续之前还有别的问题吗？
